name: Helltaker [Full Harem and Style]
description:
This LORA contains basically the whole harem and can do sfw and nsfw. A huge plus is that i managed to fit in a "official artstyle" which contains official art and offical art-like images so you can invoke that at anytime to get a more gamesque look. to invoke it i reccomend "official artstyle with (cel shading) and official art". I included a prompt S/R sweep to display the style change with a token gradient.

The trigger words section contains all of the concepts that i trained the model on.

modelVersions.name: v1
modelVersions.description: justice has some weird stuff with her sunglasses getting doubled pretty often and it really likes her red hairtie. azazel's halo cant form a ring sometimes, but thats just latent bs for you.
